,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:12:48.000Z","msg":"你阿姐話唔會「出賣」你地<br />\n但呢件事係佢搞出黎架，佢唔敢行出黎，已經係「出賣」緊你地"},{"pid":"94d62c717c0ad3e53db50e5aa7aa2a61166f9553","tid":1316392,"uid":43082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:13:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f42b4bbcd8c66b8a62df7ce6191af55f6ceb85dc","tid":1316392,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:13:59.000Z","msg":"點解「野戰」唔俾射催淚彈阿<br />\n咪為左睇你地俾人打囉<br />\n咁重裝你行動都不便啦，點保護你阿"},{"pid":"0aa189fdbe5c16f435da4351cd7442b13e1a0df5","tid":1316392,"uid":219681,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:18:19.000Z","msg":"你個宿舍係好大阿，但你返到屋企咩?<br />\n你份人工係好高阿，但你夠肥聰高咩?<br />\n你無非想屋企人安居樂業，點解唔做消防阿，又幫到人，又有使命感<br />\n<br />\n今時今日做差佬，又要俾人笑，又要驚俾人起底<br />\n班高官既屋企人，響外國Happy緊阿，你屋企人呢? 擔心緊你既安全阿。<br />\n做一隻棋子做到冇左命仔，值得咩?"},{"pid":"d06e7d5954a0f34a7953977c840ea6d4c9e45fb4","tid":1316392,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:19:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f92ba2d67086da0fbbe6cba089a5fb61c97b3fb","tid":1316392,"uid":31528,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:19:44.000Z","msg":"呢班棋子係咁用架啦<br />\n班細嘅就被人推出黎做show<br />\n大粒果啲就等食花生再領工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b5097af6b207c4184fda64d3602b657997c9cd3","tid":1316392,"uid":219681,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:20:32.000Z","msg":"你打一世工都唔會做到肥聰個位阿<br />\n佢個位只會俾自己友坐，知道嘛"},{"pid":"ad29b3f26dbb60bd511942a4f041c5ac019b82a7","tid":1316392,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:20:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ecc5e5bef60928c8748722aecacfeb5f37e5f48","tid":1316392,"uid":219681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:22:26.000Z"